  <Method>
    <Step image="">Preheat oil in deep fryer.</Step>
    <Step image="">In a medium sized mixing bowl add the flour, cornmeal, sugar, baking powder, salt, garlic powder, onion powder, paprika, and pepper.</Step>
    <Step image="Hushpuppies_hushpuppies-2.jpg">In a separate bowl, whisk the egg and buttermilk together. Add cubed butter and minced onions. Add to dry ingredients, mix well.</Step>
    <Step image="">Using 1 oz scoop, drop the batter by in the hot oil. Let cook until they are golden brown 2-3 minutes. Remove with a metal strainer on a paper toweled lined plate.</Step>
